{"tid":1405864,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突發：警方西區驅散行動 正施放催淚煙","createTime":"2019-08-04T11:26:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T11:30:58.000Z","uid":41404,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e572fcbad588035c6373d51e69289b08cc33fddc","tid":1405864,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:26:21.000Z","msg":"電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n <br />\n     較早時部分離開卑路乍灣公園集會的人士，目前已抵達皇后大道西一帶示威，並築起路障堵路。<br />\n      <br />\n     警方警告示威者盡快停止違法行為。因應現場情況，防暴警察正施放催淚煙，使用最低武力驅散示威者。<br />\n      <br />\n     警方呼籲附近一帶居民留意情況，如有需要，應關好窗戶，留在室內安全地方。 <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年8月4日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間19時24分"},{"pid":"3194122edd92899fbcce722890838690e2b1a010","tid":1405864,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:26:34.000Z","msg":"HKMAP即時地圖 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1403678\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1403678</a><br />\n<br />\n睇緊live既即刻入黎幫手報點!<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=37f37de9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n見到多狗, 即刻mark番落地圖<br />\n視乎數量就算已經報左都可以報多一次<br />\n幫手傳出去 等義士唔好再食布袋戰術<br />\nBe Water!<br />\n<br />\n已經左西環map, 幫手睇實唔好再比狗夾"},{"pid":"7b381eef1a619e43ae22c8977432c1d2ffec0132","tid":1405864,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:26:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400682.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201908%2F04%2FP2019080400682.htm&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUB%2Fhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=a7b1cef8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201908/04/P2019080400682.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cfaf8798d368793a581fe5df90cd0c0c8aba317a","tid":1405864,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislik